---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 292
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Orthodoxy-Ritual-Method=The Spiritual Master
By: Swami Sivananda
---
There is no other way for overhauling the vicious worldly Samskaras
(tendencies left from former actions) and the passionate nature of
raw, worldly-minded persons than the personal contact with and service
of the Guru.
